# Wave Snippets Development Guide

## Running the Development Server

To start the development server:

1. Navigate to the client directory:
   ```bash
   cd packages/client
   ```

2. Start the development server:
   ```bash
   yarn dev
   ```

The server will start at http://localhost:3000

## Features Available Without Firebase

- Create and edit code snippets
- Add multiple steps to your snippets
- Choose from different themes and languages
- Preview your snippets

Note: Some features like authentication, saving snippets, and exporting to GIF/video will not work without Firebase configuration. 